title: Australia's deputy PM resigns after affair with staffer
text:
Australia's deputy PM resigns after affair with staffer 8:25am EST - 01:26 
Barnaby Joyce, Australia's deputy prime minister, resigns from his post following an affair with a staffer and an allegation of harassment. David Doyle reports. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
